I love the idea of personalized skincare because we all have different needs and goals. #ad @specialme.cosmetics makes it super easy to get an effective skincare routine targeted to meet YOUR specific skincare concerns. I’ve been using their products for over a month and they have worked so well to target texture, redness, and pigmentation. My skin is also more hydrated overall- swipe to see the difference in my before and after photo taken one month apart. 🙌

I love that Special Me takes into account your skin type, environment, daily habits, lifestyle, and individual needs and then creates a set tailored for you. They include high-quality ingredients that really helped to target my specific needs. I included a look at my personalized report so you can get an idea of the results!

You can take their free skin assessment and get your own personalized routine at the link in my bio.
